data.title: Best tacos
data.text: There are two locations & most of the time we go to the College Station location off of Barron rd for convenience. But the food is always excellent, cooked to order with great waitstaff or attentive counter staff. We cut back eating here for a while & started eating at home because we were eating there almost everyday. They also have an incredibly good lunch buffet that is a bargain for the food you get.
